         MACRO
&NAME    TAG   &TRACKS=YES TRACKS -> LOCAL CONTROL OF TRACING
         GBLC  &$MTRACE            GLOBAL CONTROL OF TRACING
&NAME    DC    0H'0'               DEFINE TAG
         AIF   ('&TRACKS' NE 'YES').MEND      LOCAL AND GLOBAL MUST
         AIF   ('&$MTRACE' NE 'YES').MEND     BOTH BE 'YES' TO TRACE
         TRACER 'STATEMENT ''&NAME'' EXECUTED' GO TO IT...
.MEND    MEND
